Products.RichDescription:
At The Smokeman Brothers, our philosophy is simple. We believe the best flavours come from using the right combination of humble ingredients, traditional cooking processes and a commitment to not taking any short cuts. We take the tastiest cuts of Australian meat, season with the perfect combination of herbs and spices, and cook low and slow to give you the most tender, juiciest meat, packed full of flavour. We do the hard work of cooking for 8 hours so you can enjoy in just 5 minutes.

This delicious beef petite tender has been flame grilled then marinated and slow cooked for 8 hours in a zesty chimichurri sauce. Served with smooth pumpkin mash, green beans, oven roasted potatoes and onion jus. Smokeman by name, craftsman by nature.
